	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=23812><span id=Sage>Cani</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>43 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [3.70]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>The effect is right clicked, not proc'ed as it seems to me you are thinking.<br><br>Click and hold the left mouse button on the weapon slot with inventory open and drag it to a hotkey slot. That way you can trigger the reclaim energy effect without having to go to your inventory. Target your pet first and hit the hotkey you just made and you get a decent chunk of your mana back. :)<br><br>And I did try it before even making the post below, so I know for sure that you CAN use the effect on the Stein at level 9.<br><br>Hope this clears things up. :)</p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
